{"title":"节日彩灯","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2477","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>儿童节到了，蒋老师要同学们按照一定的规律将各色彩灯串起来悬挂在教室上方。所有彩灯串起来后成一直线。彩灯按照红、蓝、黄、绿、紫、红、蓝、黄、绿、紫、红、蓝、黄、绿、紫、……的颜色规律排列（所有彩灯一共只有这么5种颜色，如下图所示，每盏灯从左到右还进行了编号）。现在告诉你某盏彩灯的编号，请你编程计算该彩灯的颜色。</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n<img src=\"/source/codevs/codevs-2477/img/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5qb3lvaS5jbi9wcm9ibGVtL2NvZGV2cy0yNDc3L2h0dHA6Ly9jb2RldnMuY24vbWVkaWEvaW1hZ2UvMjQ3N18xLmdpZg==.gif\" style=\"max-width:700px\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入只有一行一个正整数n，表示该彩灯的编号。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出只有一行一个小写字母，这个小写字母表示该彩灯颜色英语单词的第一个字母。红、蓝、黄、绿、紫分别用小写字母r、b、y、g、p表示。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>【输入样例1】</p>\n<p>7</p>\n<p>【输入样例2】</p>\n<p>19</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>【输出样例1】</p>\n<p>b</p>\n<p>【速出样例2】</p>\n<p>g</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5&lt;=n&lt;=100000</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}